reviewText: Pleasantly surprised to find this treasure of early movies of leading men before they became stars. If you're  a movie history buff you might  get a kick out of this collection. There are no classics here but the stories held my attention.  I am satisfied with the vendor I ordered these from too.  .

WWF Strong Men (WS904)
1980s Hercules vs. The Ultimate Warrior (chain match)
01/24/88 Dino Bravo bench press angle
1980s Dino Bravo vs. Hercules
1980s Demolition vs. Powers of Pain
03/29/87 Andre the Giant vs. Hulk Hogan
